cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this dataset, please cite it."
title: "MisInfoShort-22K"
version: 1.0.0
license: CC-BY-4.0
abstract: >
  20,000 short-text samples across 5 domains and 4 label classes
  for misinformation detection research. Includes emotion triggers,
  misinfo subtypes, semantic focus, and stratified splits.
keywords:
  - misinformation
  - fake news
  - NLP
  - text classification
  - emotion detection
  - short text
  - social media
